n><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: windowtext; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt;\">0834-2580015</span><span style=\"color: windowtext; line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: windowtext; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt;\">2580111   <o:p></o:p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">◆第二章</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">组织机构及职责</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt;\">   <o:p></o:p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;\">第十条</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-a